{"tid":1545422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[港隊主場冇問題]10號銅鑼灣要人丫！！！","createTime":"2019-09-06T01:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T02:41:56.000Z","uid":163519,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"687214668e6b3cdbb43b37ff0eabcc90fc50a7f3","tid":1545422,"uid":163519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:55:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>唔好意思因為之前伊朗申請中立場所以停推，而家FIFA確認<span style=\"color: red;\">港隊主場冇問題</span>所以再推</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">10號</span></strong>香港大球場要人丫！！！香港人唔好同我講唔撐香港隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隊波仲要<strong>冇中國兩個字</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2022卡塔爾世界盃暨2023中國亞洲盃聯合外圍賽第二圈（C組）<br />\n2019年9月10日<br />\n晚上8時<br />\n<strong>香港</strong> 對 伊朗</span><br />\n<br />\n票價<br />\n成人：180元；<br />\n特惠：40元<br />\n（凡於9月9日或之前於門市或Cityline購票通購買單場門票，均可豁免Cityline購票通手續費。）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://venue.cityline.com/utsvInternet/enrollment/action/event.do?actionFwd=eventDetail&amp;event=31912&amp;activityCode=EAFF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvenue.cityline.com%2FutsvInternet%2Fenrollment%2Faction%2Fevent.do%3FactionFwd%3DeventDetail%26event%3D31912%26activityCode%3DEAFF&d=qjQisgq6tteJ1Wb%2FuF84H6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=a9eaa113\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://venue.cityline.com/utsvInternet/enrollment/action/event.do?actionFwd=eventDetail&amp;event=31912&amp;activityCode=EAFF</a> 快啲買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又話9月繼續抗爭唔好俾佢完，係咪香港大球場4萬個位都坐唔滿丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n場波又會播<span style=\"color: navy;\">義勇軍進行軍</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又可以不停叫口號（港超啲手足叫足全場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）如果有波衫記得著埋去！！好多位球員都係手足嚟，新聞都報哂喇，你唔係唔撐番佢地嘛？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"1d70ac1c2623d01f8e98bbfc7af3129e46ddc984","tid":1545422,"uid":163519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:56:13.000Z","msg":"自推十連(1/10)"},{"pid":"4986ac11e4944cda636deae14c2ba912e9431e66","tid":1545422,"uid":163519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:56:47.000Z","msg":"自推十連(2/10)"},{"pid":"f4d4696d43a617db6abdaca8d45cfc3985151e8f","tid":1545422,"uid":163519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T01:57:44.000Z","msg":"自推十連(3/10)"},{"pid":"1460bb7c06e7f75b61e89bcf4aee4e1fd7c1e3db","tid":1545422,"uid":84869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f4b4a5cdeadc200048bb620537670b1b46a876","tid":1545422,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:03:53.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1d2cf0ccee9981566599ff677cf2bd57a9a2f71","tid":1545422,"uid":163519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:04:34.000Z","msg":"自推十連(4/10)"},{"pid":"fb681d74da1ac8da1b8bdeb2e1f3fb9437ae34fa","tid":1545422,"uid":163519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T02:07:10.000Z","msg":"自推十連(5/10)"},{"pid":"faaf3b7fdca9df6326d94941ddcc4fb57840af41","tid":1545422,"uid":45983,"like":0,"d